    <result xml:space="preserve">(the scroll of rezrov)&#x000A;While "REZROV" can be clearly read at the top of the scroll, the rest is in some arcane script you (and the people of your village) are unfamiliar with.&#x000A;&#x000A;&gt;</result>
    <commentary xml:space="preserve"></commentary>
    <changed>NO</changed>
